title: CarX Drift Racing Online v1.0.2
description: CarX Drift Racing is a racing simulator dedicated to the motorsport of drifting. Legendary cars, detailed tuning settings and a real-time multiplayer mode in full HD at 60 fps. All this awaits you in the PC version of this popular mobile game! Key features:u25cf Over 10 tracks designed specially for driftingu25cf 30 cars with the option for detailed physics settingsu25cf Support for gamepads and gaming wheelsu25cf Real-time multiplayer mode with up to 8 players per game session
